input: Which driver ranked the first in the Canadian Grand Prix in 2007? Please give his reference name.
sql: select drivers.driverref from drivers join results on drivers.driverid = results.driverid join races on results.raceid = races.raceid where races.name = 'Canadian Grand Prix' and year = 2007 order by drivers.driverref asc limit 1

input: List the names of closed event as "game" that was closed from 3/15/2019 to 3/20/2020.
sql: select event_name from event where type = 'Closed' and event_date between 3/15/2019 and 3/20/2020

input: Mention the category of events which were held at MU 215.
sql: select event_name from event where location = 'MU 215'

input: Was the patient a man or a women whose ALT glutamic pylvic transaminase status got 9 on 1992-6-12?
sql: select sex from patient where id = 9 and sex = 'M' and sex = 'F'

input: For the patients whose total cholesterol is higher than normal, how many of them have a negative measure of degree of coagulation?
sql: select count ( * ) from examination join patient on examination.id = patient.id where examination.diagnosis = 'Non-Normal'

input: What is the average index of the lactate dehydrogenase (LDH) for all patients with lactate dehydrogenase (LDH) within the normal range.
sql: select avg ( examination.diagnosis ) from examination join patient on examination.id = patient.id join laboratory on laboratory.id = patient.id where laboratory.ldh = 'lactate dehydrogenase' and examination.diagnosis = 'Normal'

input: Write the full name of the member who spent money for water, veggie tray and supplies and include the cost of it.
Among the users who obtained the "Organizer" badges, calculate the percentage of users who are teenagers.
sql: select users.age , count ( * ) from badges join users on badges.userid = users.id where badges.name = 'Organizer' group by users.id

input: What was the final score for the match on September 24, 2008, in the Belgian Jupiler League between the home team and the away team?
Among the patients with the normal level of triglyceride, how many of them have other symptoms observed?
sql: select count ( distinct symptoms ) from examination join patient on examination.id = patient.id where examination.diagnosis = 'Normal'

input: Identify the gender of the superhero who has the ability of Phoenix Force.
sql: select gender.gender from superhero join gender on superhero.id = gender.id join superpower on superhero.id = superpower.id where superpower.power_name = 'Phoenix Force'

input: Calculate the percentage of carcinogenic molecules with triple bonded Hidrogen atoms.
sql: select count ( * ) from atom join connected on atom.atom_id = connected.atom_id join bond on connected.bond_id = bond.bond_id where bond.bond_type = 'Hidrogen'

input: Please list top three molecules that have single bonds between two atoms and are not carcinogenic in alphabetical order.
sql: select molecule.molecule_id from molecule join bond on molecule.molecule_id = bond.molecule_id where bond.bond_id = 2 order by molecule.molecule_id asc

input: Among all the lap records set on various circuits, what is the time for the fastest one?
sql: select time from laptimes order by milliseconds desc limit 1

input: List the superheroes from Marvel Comics who have the super power of 'Super Strength'.
sql: select superhero.superhero_name from superhero join hero_power on superhero.id = hero_power.hero_id join superpower on superhero.id = superpower.id where superpower.power_name = 'Super Strength'

input: Provide ID, sex and age of patient who has blood glucose (GLU) not within normal range but with total cholesterol(T-CHO) within normal range.
What is the total number of non-chartered schools in the county of Los Angeles with a percent (%) of eligible free meals for grades 1 through 12 that is less than 0.18%?
When was the first time did Kevin Constant have his highest crossing score? Give the date.
sql: select distinct player_attributes.date from player join player_attributes on player.player_api_id = player_attributes.player_api_id where player.player_name = 'Kevin Constant' order by player_attributes.crossing desc limit 1

input: For all cards illustrated by Jim Pavelec. and describe the text of the ruling of these cards. Do these cards have missing or degraded properties and values.
sql: select rulings.text from cards join rulings on cards.uuid = rulings.uuid where cards.artist = 'Jim Pavelec' or cards.text = 'degraded'

input: Please list the lap records for the circuits in Italy.
sql: select laptimes.lap from circuits join laptimes on circuits.circuitid = laptimes.lap where circuits.country = 'Italy'

input: Among the patients who have a normal platelet level, how many of them have other symptoms observed?
sql: select count ( distinct symptoms ) from examination join patient on examination.id = patient.id where examination.diagnosis = 'Normal'

input: What is the description about the ruling of card "Condemn"?
sql: select rulings.text from rulings join cards on rulings.uuid = cards.uuid where cards.name = 'Condemn'

input: On what year did the youngest driver had his first qualifying race? Also state the name, date and time of the race.
sql: select drivers.driverid , races.date , races.time from drivers join qualifying on drivers.driverid = qualifying.driverid join races on qualifying.raceid = races.raceid order by drivers.dob asc limit 1

input: What is the percentage of carbon in double-bond molecules?
sql: select molecule.label from molecule join bond on molecule.molecule_id = bond.molecule_id where bond.bond_type = 'double-bond'

input: Among the patients with the normal level of triglyceride, how many of them have other symptoms observed?
sql: select count ( distinct symptoms ) from examination join patient on examination.id = patient.id where examination.diagnosis = 'Normal'

input: For all the set of cards that has Japanese translation, what is the percentage of them are only available in non-foil?
sql: select count ( * ) from sets join set_translations on sets.code = set_translations.setcode where set_translations.language = 'Japanese' and sets.isnonfoilonly = 1

input: What kind of currency did the customer paid at 16:25:00 in 2012/8/24?
Which country is the league Italy Serie A from?
sql: select country.name from country join league on country.id = league.country_id where league.name = 'Italy Serie A'

input: For patients with abnormal platelet level, state the number of patients with lower than normal range. How is it compare to the number of patients with higher than normal range?
Consider the average difference between K-12 enrollment and 15-17 enrollment of schools that are locally funded, list the names and DOC type of schools which has a difference above this average.
In comments with score between 1 to 5, list down the display names of the users with 0 down votes.
sql: select userdisplayname from comments where score between 1 and 5

input: What is the lap record set by Lewis Hamilton in a Formula_1 race?
sql: select laptimes.lap from results join laptimes on results.driverid = laptimes.driverid join races on results.raceid = races.raceid join drivers on results.driverid = drivers.driverid where drivers.forename = 'Lewis' and drivers.surname = 'Hamilton'

input: Among the cards with converted mana cost higher than 5 in the set Coldsnap, how many of them have unknown power?
sql: select count ( * ) from cards where convertedmanacost > 5 and power = 'Unknown'

input: Name the atoms' elements that form bond TR000_2_3.
sql: select atom.element from atom join connected on atom.atom_id = connected.atom_id join bond on connected.bond_id = bond.bond_id where bond.bond_id = 'TR000_2_3'

input: At present, calculate for the player's age who have a sprint speed of no less than 97 between 2013 to 2015.
sql: select player.birthday from player join player_attributes on player.player_api_id = player_attributes.player_api_id where player_attributes.sprint_speed between 2013 and 2015
